cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper focuses on developing robust and safe learning methods for autonomous vehicles, which involves reinforcement learning and control. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves a scenario of autonomous driving, which suggests the possibility of cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as relevant categories.
